AAB.CO.summary: Aalborg Boldspilklub A/S engages in the sports and entertainment activities in Denmark. The company operates a professional football club; and Aalborg Portland Park stadium. It offers tickets to football games; and merchandise. The company also provides toy clothes, collections, clothing, children toys, and accessories online. Aalborg Boldspilklub A/S was founded in 1885 and is based in Aalborg, Denmark.

ASGRF.summary: Astralis A/S operates as an esports company. It owns three esports teams under the Astralis, Origen, and Future FC brands. The company was formerly known as Astralis Group A/S and changed its name to Astralis A/S in April 2021. Astralis A/S was founded in 2016 and is based in Copenhagen, Denmark.

D2V.F.summary: PARKEN Sport & Entertainment A/S operates in the sports industry in Denmark. The company operates a football stadium and club, and office properties. It is also involved in the operation of Lalandia holiday and activity centers; and the rental and sale of holiday homes. The company was founded in 1991 and is based in Copenhagen, Denmark.

SIF.CO.summary: Silkeborg IF Invest A/S operates a professional football club in Denmark. It also engages in the rental and operation of business area; and hotel and conference activities. The company was formerly known as SIF Football Support A/S and changed its name to Silkeborg IF Invest A/S in 2008. Silkeborg IF Invest A/S was founded in 1917 and is based in Silkeborg, Denmark.

TIV.CO.summary: Tivoli A/S engages in entertainment and recreational activities. The company operates and maintains gardens. The company offers rides, games, shows, events, and concerts. It also operates restaurants, as well as online casino through Danske Spi. Tivoli A/S was founded in 1843 and is based in Copenhagen, Denmark.
